title: Bunkercast XVIII: PI Calls and Virtual Draft
itunes:title: Bunkercast XVIII: PI Calls and Virtual Draft
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including the latest with the PI calls, the draft taking place virtually and a potential new broadcaster on the scene.
